Hi @Léo, thanks for putting together the information. A few comments:
• Which env have you used for building/developing this application? I see a link to the prod-app on the doc (which is broken for me, must be on your private space) but have you developed it on Prod and published this as a private app?
• Do you have the FLA and can you add it to the confluence along with the development component details?
• Can you start collecting/putting together the metadata mentioned on the checklist of your doc?
Env prod, how can I change space on AI hub ? What is FLA?

I think we should plan on using the lower env for application development (preferably UAT, not Prod). Once the application looks good, it can be promoted to Prod. FLA is nothing but Field Level Accuracy for each fields present in the application.
